source: A group of students from a rival school are roaming the streets. Impart your teachings upon them.
target: Eskola aurkari bateko ikasleak kaleetan harat-honat dabiltza. Erakutsiezu ikasi duzuna.

source: Accidents happen so fast. Think about it.
target: Istripuak oso azkar gertatzen dira. Pentsa ezazu.

source: Advanced age benefits wisdom, and also bestows a wealth of experience in efficiency.
target: Adinean gora egiteak jakituria ematen dizu, eta izugarri eraginkor egiten zaitu.

source: Amidst the blizzard's concealment, you face a solitary target, but watch out for lurking threats.
target: Ezkutatu ahal izateko haizetea aprobetxatuta, etsai bakarti bati aurre egiten diozu, baina kontuz ezkutuko mehatxuekin.

source: An ideal spot, with a killer view, to bring the entire city to its knees in one fell swoop.
target: Bista zoragarriak dituen leku ederra, kolpe bakarrean hiri guztia belauniko jartzeko modukoa.

source: As a security agent, expel the trespassers from the parking.
target: Segurtasun agente moduan, baimenik gabe parkinean sartu direnak botako dituzu.

source: As the cold empowers your fists, seize the perfect opportunity to take down a horde of adversaries.
target: Ukabil izoztuak dituzunez, aprobetxatu egoera aurkari horda bat pikutara bidaltzeko.

source: Assess your strength against all kinds of fighters.
target: Frogatu zure indarra mota askotariko borrokalarien aurka.

source: Attain enlightenment by siphoning the life force of your opponents.
target: Ailegatu zaitez argitasun egoera batera zure arerioen bizi-indarra xurgatuz.

source: Back to school, demonstrate the skills you have acquired.
target: Eskolara itzuli zara, erakutsi ikasi dituzun abileziak.

source: Be swift like the wind. Effortlessly sweep away your enemies.
target: Izan haizea bezain azkarra. Deuseztatu zure etsaiak ahaleginik egin gabe.

source: Before reaching Fajar, you have to get through his crew.
Blood for blood, but do not get sliced.
target: Odola odol truk, baina ez utzi motz zaitzaten.

source: Brawl against Fajar and gangsters from the filth of The Squats.
target: Borrokatu Fajar-en eta okupa eremu higuingarriko gangsterren aurka.

source: Climb your way up and take the high ground.
target: Igo zaitez eta eskuratu goiko eremua.

source: Combat is a distinct form of artistic expression, where your fists become the brush that paints your masterpiece.
target: Borroka espresio artistiko bat da bere hortan, zure maisulana margotzeko erabilitako pintzelak zure ukabilak direlarik.

source: Confront your own transgressions and bury the shame deep within yourself.
target: Egin aurre zure bekatuei eta gorde ezazu lotsa zure sakonenean.

source: Crash the party and take over the Dance Floor in a powerful performance.
target: Izorratu festa: zeureganatu dantzalekua ikuskizun paregabearekin.

source: Defeat all the rain worshippers, and find your sun.
target: Garaitu euriaren gurtzaile guztiak, eta topatu zure eguzkia.

source: Defy your fate. Overwhelm those who dare obstruct your path, or die trying.
target: Desafiatu zure patua. Gainditu zure bidean oztopatzen zaituztenak, edo hil saiatzen.

source: Demonstrate to the rookies what a true master is capable of.
target: Erakutsi hasiberriei benetako maisua zertarako den gai.

source: Destroy Jinfeng's conspiracy and her minions.
target: Deuseztatu Jinfeng-en konspirazioa eta bere lekaioak.

source: Do the city a favor and take over the place.
target: Egin hiriari mesede bat leku hau zeureganatuz.

source: Don't let your dreams be dreams! Enforce the law in this working escalator and assert authority.
target: Zure ametsak ez daitezela amets soilik izan! Ezarri zure legea eskailera mekaniko hauetan eta gailendu zaitez.

source: Earn your place as the greatest Sifu, by triumphing over your predecessors in this ultimate challenge.
target: Lortu ezazu Sifu onenaren lekua, zure aurretik zeudenak garaituz azken erronka honetan.

source: Eliminate the purple mist dealers who are peddling their product in the parking area and clean them out.
target: Deuseztatu aparkalekuan laino morea banatzen ari diren guztiak eta garbitu eremua.

source: Emerge as the supreme fighter in the city, taking on all the elite warriors.
target: Aldarrikatu hiriko borrokalaririk onena zarela, eliteko gerlari guztiak garaituz.

source: Encircled by the security team, stand your ground and stop their attempts to bring you down.
target: Segurtasun taldeak inguratu zaitu. Mantendu zure posizioa eta ekidin zu lurrera botatzeko saiakerak.

source: Engulfed by a strong aroma, disorientation sets in. Get a hold of yourself and fight back!
target: Lurrin indartsu batek inguratzen zaitu eta nahasmenak irensten zaitu. Osatu zaitez eta kontraerasotu!

source: Enter this ultimate rain fight and defeat them all.
target: Har ezazu parte euripeko azken borroka honetan eta garaitu itzazu denak.

source: Enveloped by the haze of purple mist unleashed upon you by tattooed thugs, fight off the hallucination by eliminating the main threats.
target: Tatuajedun morroi horiek botatako laino more arraro batek bilduta zaituela, egin aurre haluzinazioei eta deuseztatu mehatxu nagusiak.

source: Every art connoisseur is well aware of the positioning required to truly immerse oneself in the essence of a piece.
target: Artean aditua den edonork badaki zeinen garrantzitsua den ikuspegia artelan batean benetan murgiltzeko.

source: Exhibit your solid professionalism as you take everyone down before they even realise what's going on.
target: Erakutsi zure profesionaltasun irmoa: eraitsi itzazu guztiak zer gertatzen ari den ohartu baino lehen.

source: Fend off Sean's fighters and their burning heat.
target: Egin Sean-en borrokalarien eta beraien bero itogarriaren aurka.

source: Fight your way down the silicon bowels of the tower.
target: Egin ezazu zure bidea dorrearen siliziozko erraietan behera.

source: Find the artists. Get rid of them. Fast.
target: Aurkitu artistak. Kendu itzazu zure bidetik. Azkar.

source: Find your place at the top by skillfully battling your way upstream.
target: Lortu goian dagokizun lekua bidean zehar trebeki borroka eginez.

source: For once, you were chosen as the target. Make them regret it.
target: Behingoz, zu hautatu zaituzte jomugatzat. Damutu daitezela.

source: Fresh recruits trained hard to reach your level. Show them why you're still the undisputed boss.
target: Errekruta hauek gogor entrenatu dute zure mailara ailegatzeko. Erakutsiezu zergatik zaren oraindik nagusi ukaezina.

source: Give Sifu another chance to change his untimely fate.
target: Emaiozu zure Sifuari bere patu goiztiarra aldatzeko beste aukera bat.

source: Grab and toss them around, show all your moves.
In It for the Long Run
In a Data Center Far Far Away
In order to access the mainframe, hack a path through your enemies.
target: Zerbitzarian sartu aurretik, etsaien artetik bidea ireki beharko duzu.

source: It Is Not a Game of Death
It's pure chaos outside, a mob is trying to make its way in. Prevent them from getting past the entrance at all costs.
target: Kanpoan kaos hutsa da, jende-multzo batek erakusketara sartu nahi du. Ekidin ezazu barrura sartzea ahal duzun bezala.

source: Just a Walk in the Park
Keep your ground and stay inside the square.
target: Mantendu zure posizioa eta ez atera karratutik.

source: Leaders of the Club all think they can take you down on their own. Deny them any opportunity to land a single blow on you.
target: Klubeko liderrek alde batera utzi zaitzaketela uste dute. Ez iezaiezu utzi zu behin ere jotzen.

source: Lost souls seek unique paths. With a meticulous plan, you can guide them towards their redemption.
target: Galdutako espirituek bide bakarrak bilatzen dituzte. Plan zehatz batekin, beraien erredentziora gidatu ditzakezu.

source: Make a mess in every corner of the kitchen.
Make a mess, and survive too.
Make your way to the center of the stage and claim the spotlight for yourself only!
target: Ireki ezazu eszenatoki erdiranzko bidea eta hartu fokua zuretzat bakarrik!
Agian ez da ibilaldi bat bakarrik

source: Move up and pick your targets one by one.
Now's your time. Infiltrate the gathering and identify the big shots to take them down.
target: Orain da zure garaia. Infiltratu zaitez bileran, identifikatu nagusiak eta deusezta itzazu.

source: On the precipice of your demise, prove to these ruffians that you won't die alone.
target: Zure azken hatsaren ertzean, erakutsi gaizkile horiei ez zarela zu bakarrik hilko.

source: Perched 40 feet above the ground, encircled by enemies, no way out. Get to work.
target: 12 metroko altueran zaude, etsaiez inguratuta, ez dago irteerarik. Hasi lanean.

source: Practice visualising your enemies, concentrate, and defeat each and every one of them.
target: Praktikatu zure etsaiak ikustea, kontzentratu eta garaitu itzazu guztiak.

source: Practice your cleaning techniques by getting rid of the dirty fighters within your Wuguan.
target: Praktikatu zure garbitze teknikak eta kendu begi bistatik zure Wuguan-ean sartu diren gaizkile zikin hauek.

source: Prove these street fighters they do not know who they are up against.
target: Erakutsi kaleko borrokalari hauei ez dakitela noren kontra ari diren.

source: Put a stop to the shady stuff that's going down around the Bike Shelter.
target: Geldi ezazu bizikleten aparkalekutik hurbil egiten ari diren negozio iluna.

source: Put an end to the relentless gang violence.
Put an end to your bloodshed by vanquishing the five traitors in this ultimate ordeal.
target: Garaitu bost traidoreak eta bukatu zure sarraskia azken borroka honetan.

source: Raid the place, arrest the suspects and their boss.
target: Egin sarekada, atxilotu susmagarriak eta beraien nagusia.

source: Relive the infamous night that crowned you as the new Earth Sifu.
target: Bizi berriz Lurreko Sifu berri bezala koroatua izan zinen gau tamalgarria.

source: Ride the high of beating your enemies as you ascend and descend the Warehouse.
target: Gozatu Biltegian gora eta behera zabiltzan bitartean etsaiak garaitzearen zirraraz.

source: Rival their weapons with your bare hands.
She's trying to leave. Do not let her go, do whatever it takes.
target: Ihes egiten saiatzen ari da. Ez ezaiozu utzi, egizu beharrezkoa dena.

source: Show the ones looking for you they should have stayed home.
target: Erakutsi zure bila datozenei hobe zutela etxean geratzea.

source: Some enemies don't give up easily, time to teach them a valuable lesson.
target: Etsai batzuk ez dute erraz amore ematen, lezio garrantzitsua irakasteko garaia da.

source: Some partygoers have overstayed their welcome. Show them the way out.
target: Festazale batzuk ongietorriaz gehiegi baliatzen ari dira. Erakutsi iezazuezu kanporako bidea.

source: Spar with Kuroki and her favorite artists and servants.
target: Egin borroka Kuroki eta bere artista eta zerbitzari gustukoenekin.

source: Stand up to Yang and the renowned guardians of The Sanctuary.
target: Borrokatu Yang eta Santutegiko zaindari entzutetsuen aurka.

source: Stay sharp to survive the relentless assault of armed guards.
target: Egon adi zaindari armadunen eraso lazgarriei bizirauteko.

source: Stay strong. Stay young. Stay up there.
target: Jarraitu indartsu. Jarraitu gazte. Jarraitu hor.

source: Steel yourself to overcome each and every adversary who dares to obstruct your path of vengeance.
target: Izan indartsua eta garaitu zure eta mendekuaren arteko bidean jartzera ausartzen den edozein aurkari.

source: Strength lies in stability. Protect this sanctuary at all costs.
target: Indarra egonkortasunean datza. Babestu santutegi hau kosta ahala kosta.

source: Strengthen your spirit and body against Sean and his cult.
target: Indartu zure espiritua eta gorputza Sean eta bere sektaren aurka.

source: Success lies in precision, swiftness, and efficiency.
target: Arrakasta gakoak zehaztasuna, azkartasuna eta eraginkortasuna dira.

source: Survive the gang's set-up and clean the corridor.
target: Biziraun bandaren tranapri eta garbitu korridorea.

source: Take a tour of the Gallery and get rid of the bothersome visitors disrupting the immersive experience.
target: Eman ezazu bueltaxka bat museoan zehar eta kendu paretik zure esperientzia zapuzten duten bisitari gogaikarri guzti horiek.

source: Take down the clan, vengeance is nothing to be trifled with.
target: Deuseztatu klana, mendekua ez da jolasa.

source: That is your entrance, make it count and prove your worth.
target: Hori da zure sarrera. Aprobetxatu aukera eta erakutsi zure balioa.

source: The Dance Floor has been taken over by a mob. Dive right into the chaos and whack them around.
target: Jendetza bat dago dantzalekuan. Sar zaitez kaosean eta knaporatu itzazu denak.

source: The audience is not only here to party. They want a piece of the fight.
target: Hemengo ikusleak ez daude ikusteko soilik. Borrokan parte hartu nahi dute.

source: The devil is in the details. Even the most confined corners of the Gallery demand meticulous cleaning.
target: Xehetasunetan dago gakoa. Museoko txokorik ezkutuenek ere garbitasun sakona behar dute.

source: The epitome of survival of the fittest.
The first step to being respected, is to look respectable. Get this warehouse back in order.
target: Errespetatua izateko lehenengo pausua, errespetuzkoaren itxura izatea da. Berrezarri biltegi honetako ordena.

source: The gang is back for more. They are here for you.
target: Banda gehiagoren bila dator. Zuregana datoz.

source: The smell of blood stays strong, even in the snow.
target: Odolaren kirats sarkorra dago, baita elurretan ere.

source: The spirits are relentless, but the brave yellow puncher won't back down.
target: Espirituak gupidagabeak dira, baina figura ausart horiak ez dio ukabilkadak emateari utziko.

source: The stairwell might need a makeover after you are done. Paint it red.
target: Zuk bukatu eta gero eskailerak berriro margotu beharko dira. Margo itzazu gorriz.

source: The thieves are leaving with your Lion Dance equipment! Take out the leaders that are wearing a costume.
target: Lapurrak zure Lehoiaren Dantza ekipamenduarekin doaz! Deuseztatu mozorroturik dauden liderrak.

source: Their pace may be slow , yet they remain deadly. Avoid being overwhelmed and target the strongest threats.
target: Mugimenduak motelak izan arren, hilkorrak dira. Ez zaitez larritu eta hasi mehatxu indartsuenetatik.

source: These artists seek to challenge you during your stroll.
target: Artista hauek desafioa jo nahi dizute zure ibilaldian zehar.

source: These people are not only here for the view.
target: Pertsona hauek ez dira bistengatik bakarrik etorri.

source: These streets are ill-famed. Change that.
target: Kale hauek ospe oso txarra dute. Alda ezazu hori.

source: They are afraid, be a person of focus, commitment and sheer will!
target: Beldurtuta daude, beraz badakizu: kontzentrazioa, borondatea eta konpromezua!

source: They didn't expect any security. Catch them off guard and stop them from getting too comfortable.
target: Ez zuten inongo segurtasunik espero. Harrapa itzazu ustekabean, erosoegi jarri baino lehen.

source: They multiply and multiply until you are overwhelmed. Be the one to face them head on.
target: Gainezka egin arte ari dira biderkatzen. Ausartu zaitez beraiei aurre egiten.

source: They've spread around the garage, chase them down to eliminate everyone you see.
target: Aparkaleku giztian zehar daude, jarraitu eta deusezta ezazu ikusten duzun oro.

source: This area is for DJs only, keep Sean and his cronies away from the booth.
target: Eremu hau DJentzat soilik da, ez utzi Sean edo bere lekaioak kabinara hurbiltzen ere.

source: This is your place. Do not let anyone question you are the boss.
target: Hau zure lekua da. Ez dezala inork zalantzan jarri zu nagusia zarenik.

source: This place needs a cleaning, help people get their homes back.
target: Leku honek garbiketa bat behar du, erakutsi jendeari etxerako bidea.

source: To endure the cold, stay warm by beating down your enemies.
target: Hotzari aurre egiteko, epeldu zaitez zure etsaiei egurra emanez.

source: To reach the pinnacle, one must rely solely on their fists.
target: Gailurrera ailegatzeko, ukabiletaz bakarrik fida gaitezke.

source: Two women, standing together yet torn apart. Make your way through this extraordinary living exhibition.
target: Bi emakume elkarrekin, baina aldi berean bananduta. Ireki bidea erakusketa harrigarri honetan zehar.

source: Unnatural entities are lurking in the garage's shadows, you better get them before they get you.
target: Antinaturalak diren entitate batzuk daude aparkalekuko itzaletan begira. Hobe duzu beraiek aurkitzea, beraiek zu aurkitu baino lehen.

source: Use your Kung Fu to prevent the beast's spirits from invading the Heliport.
target: Erabili zure Kung Fu mugimenduak piztiaren espirituek heliportua berenganatzea ekiditeko.

source: Use your imagination to secure the place.
Vandalism strikes at the very core of your being. Stop the ruffians and protect the precious artwork.
target: Bandalismoak benetan haserretzen zaitu. Geldiarazi gaizkile horiek eta babestu artelan preziatuak.

source: Waves after waves, earn your title and elevate yourself.
target: Olatuak olatuen ondotik, lortu zure titulua eta goratu zaitez.

source: With your Kung Fu, even a humble snowball can turn into into a lethal weapon.
target: Zure Kung Fu mugimenduekin, elur-bola arrunt bat ere arma hilkor bihurtu daitezke.

source: Witnesses are a hassle, eliminate them swiftly before they call too many reinforcements.
target: Lekukoak amorragarriak dira, deusezta itzazu azkar, lagun gehiagori deitu baino lehen.

source: You Do Not Talk About This Club
target: Ezin da Klubari buruz hitz egin

source: You are the one. Prove it.
target: Zu bakarrik zara gai. Erakutsi ezazu.

source: You heard about an underground fighting club where people come to get thrashed. Join in and claim your share of the brawl.
target: Elkarri muturrak berotzeko dagoen borroka klub klandestino bati buruz zerbait entzun duzu. Sartu zaitez eta eskatu dagokizun egurra.

source: You only get one chance, but if you do it right, one is enough.
target: Aukera bakarra duzu, baina ongi egiten baduzu, bakarra aski da.

source: You received an invitation to the Car Club! Exploit this opportunity to bring them down.
target: Autoen kluberako gonbidapena jaso duzu! Aprobetxatu aukera hau eta deusezta itzazu.

source: You're not sure why everyone is looking at you like that. Unleash your wild side and and show them how to party.
target: Ez zaude ziur zergatik ari zaizkizun denak modu horretan begiratzen. Askatu zure alde basatia eta erakutsiezu nola egiten den dantza.

source: You're not that big, but you are that tough.
target: Ez zara handiegiegia, baina oso gogorra zara.

source: Your power is unmatched by any fighter in the entire galaxy.
target: Galaxia guztian ez dago zure boterearen parekorik duen borrokalaririk.

source: Change menus and subtitles language through the game.
target: Aldatu jokoko menu eta azpitituluen hizkuntza.

source: Change the opacity of subtitle background.
Enable/Disable sounds linked to the gameplay events.
Set the audio output format based on your audio setup.
target: Ezarri audio irteera formatua zure sistemaren arabera.

source: : Align HUD markers to the edges of your screen
target: : Lerrokatu HUD markagailuak zure pantailaren ertzekin

source: and the other doesn't want to fight anymore.
target: eta besteek ez dute borroka gehiago egin nahi.

source: And to restore that which once was.
target: Eta nozbait izan zena berriz izan dadila.

source: At least that's what I believed.
But that suffering, it was for something.
target: Baina sufrimendu hori zerbaitegatik izan zen.

source: But then, during my darkest days,
But what if I take it from you?
By returning here tonight, you've given me a second chance.
target: Gaur gauean hona itzuliz, bigarren aukera bat eman didazu.

source: Don't be shy, come closer so I can get a better look at you.
target: Ez izan lotsarik, zatoz honago, hurbilagotik ikus zaitzadan.

source: For whom does the bell toll?
target: Norengatik ari ote dira ezkilak jotzen?

source: He never cared about us, he cast me out,
target: Inoiz ez zen gugatik arduratu, bota egin ninduen,

source: Helpless, like the night I killed your father.
target: Babesgabe, zure aita hil nuen gauean bezala.

source: I am sorry for what happened to you.
I do not want to fight you.
target: Ez dut zurekin borroka egin nahi.

source: I have spent eight long years preparing for this.
target: Zortzi urte luze eman ditut honetarako prestatzen.

source: I should never have taught you.
I'm certain Yang would be thrilled to see you again.
target: Ziur nago Yang zu ikusteaz poztuko dela.

source: In the end you're still that same child I knew.
target: Azken finean, ezagutzen nuen haur bera izaten jarraitzen duzu.

source: It represents a school for the weak and feeble.
target: Ahul eta makalen eskola ordezkatzen du.

source: It's the only way to save them, Sifu!
target: Beraiek salbatzeko bide bakarra da, Sifu!

source: Kuroki has long since abandoned this life of violence and bloodshed.
target: Kuroki-k aspaldi utzi zuen indarkeriaz betetako bizitza odoltsua.

source: Look at your face, not even a scar.
target: Begira zure aurpegiari, ez duzu orbain bakar bat ere.
Ez... mesedez, mesedez... geldi zaitez nirekin!

source: Now leave or be forced to.
target: Zoaz orain edo derrigortu beharko zaitut.

source: Sifu's lineage ends here with your death.
target: Sifuren leinua hemen zurekin bukatzen da.

source: The bell tolls for you, the Guardians' legacy.
target: Ezkilak zuregatik ari dira jotzen, Zaindarien leinuagatik.

source: This time I will do what I must.
Time has passed since the days I trained you.
Unfortunately, I don't think you'll have that opportunity.
target: Zoritxarrez, ez dut uste aukera hori izango duzunik.

source: We did something for the people. We shared.
target: Zerbait egin genuen jende honegatik. Elkarbanatu egin dugu.

source: What would you do to save the people you love from the inevitable?
target: Zer egingo zenuke maite duzun jendea saihestezina denetik salbatzeko?

source: Will you fear death, once again?
target: Heriotzari beldurra izango diozu berriro ere?
Ez zenioke heriotzari berari erronka botako?

source: Wouldn't you cross every line? Break every rule?
target: Ez zenuke lerro oro pasatuko? Arau oro puskatuko?

source: You failed to honor your oath.
You know why I'm here, don't you?
You sound like the frightened one to me.
target: Beldurra duena zu zarela iruditzen zait.

source: You two have a lot of catching up to do.
You want to erase it all?
You were supposed to guard the talisman, not steal it!
target: Talismana babestu egin behar zenuen, ez lapurtu!

source: You're here in front of me, only because of this pendant.
target: Hemen zaude, nire aurrean, zintzilikario horri esker bakarrik.

source: Your family is certainly full of mysteries.
your father revealed his true self.
target: zure aitak bere benetako izaera erakutsi zuen.

source: {ListenerGender}|gender(He, She) who has Kung-Fu and Wude, makes the other know {ListenerGender}|gender(he, she) can break him
target: Kung-Fu eta Wude-a duenak, besteari jakinarazten dio deuseztu dezakeela.

source: {ListenerGender}|gender(His, Her) hands go out like lightning,
target: Bere eskuak tximistak bezala itzaltzen dira.

source: Shame I'll have to throw you back through it.
target: Zelako pena da hortik bueltan bidali behar izatea.

source:
"Your recent medical exam shows you're doing well. It's vital you continue your treatment. I shall return again in a few weeks to check on you.
Stay safe,
Yang"
target:
"Zure azken mediku azterketak ongi zaudela dio. Tratamenduarekin jarraitzea berebizikoa duzu. Aste batzuk barru itzuliko naiz zer moduz zauden ikusteko.
Zaindu,
Yang"

source: A passkey for a room at the Sanctuary.
Difficult to stop him. He can take hits, and he still tries to grab me. I should avoid his attacks and strike him the moment I have the opportunity.
target: Zaila da bera geldiaraztea. Kolpatuta ere, ni hartzen saiatzen jarraituko du. Bere erasoak ekidin eta aukera dudan momentuan eman behar nioke kolpea.

source: Drug money. Dirty money. No doubt blood money too.
target: Drogen dirua. Diru zikina. Odolez zikindutako dirua zalantzarik gabe.

source: He works for a gang as a botanist, and never leaves that warehouse.
target: Banda batean botanikari bezala ari da lanean, ez da inoiz biltegitik ateratzen.

source: He's the one who cut my throat that night. He's first on my list.
target: Bera da gau hartan nire zintzurra ebaki zuena. Nire zerrendako lehenengoa da.

source: I found this note stuck on a door blocking my way into the warehouse.
target: Ohar hau aurkitu dut biltegirako bidea blokeatzen zidan atean.

source: If I can get it open this will be a useful shortcut.
target: Hau irekitzeko gai banintz, lasterbide ederra litzateke.

source: It looks like someone's private room.
It's where I hope to face Sean. I overheard one of the thugs talking about betting on something going down there tonight.
target: Sean-en aurka aritzea espero dudan lekua da. Bere langile harroputzetako bati entzun diot aposturen bat zutela gaur gauean.

source: Most of them are completely high. They're controlled by the gangsters here.
target: Gehienak erabat drogatuta daude. Inguruko gangster-en kontrolpean daude.

source: Moving through the warehouse will be a lot easier with these keys.
target: Giltza hauekin, biltegian zehar ibiltzea askoz errazagoa izango da.

source: The drug produced here. It appeared a few years after the death of my father, and its use has increased dramatically throughout the city.
target: Droga hemen ekoizten da. Nire aitaren heriotzaren ondoren urte gutxitara agertu zen, eta honen erabilera hiri guztira zabaldu da.

source: The flower used to create the "Purple Mist".
target: Laino morea" sortzeko erabiltzen den lorea."

source: There are no details about what kind of illness Fajar appears to have.
target: Ez dago Fajar-ek izan dezakeen gaixotasunari buruzko xehetasunik.

source:
Theres only one place in the world you can find the flower, Fajar's creation.
It's hard to believe Fajar cares for anything, let alone flowers.
target:
Lore hau, Fajar-en sorkuntza, aurki dezakezun leku bakarra da.
Sinestezina da Fajar-ek zerbait zain dezakeenik, eta gutxiago lore bat.

source: These tattooed twins seem to be in charge of the drug lab's security.
target: Biki tatuajedun hauek dirudite droga laborategiko segurtasun arduradunak.

source: This gate keeps their dirty money safe.
target: Ate honek beraien diru zikina salbu mantentzen du.

source:
This used to be an industrial district. Once work dried up everyone left.
The gangs took over and it became a no-go zone.
target:
Hau lehenago industria-barruti bat zen. Lana bukatu zenean, denek alde egin zuten.
Bandek eremu guztia berenganatu zuten eta ez etortzeko lekua bihurtu da.

source: Thugs. And yet they still know how to fight. Street experience, I guess.
target: Kirtenak, baina badakite nola borrokatu. Kaleko esperientzia, nik uste.

source:
An infamous night club in the city.
The owner is a good friend of Sean's, I remember his father complaining about the guys attendance at school.
It appears the clientele aren't much better.
target:
Hiriko gau-klub zitala.
Jabea Sean-en lagun mina da. Bere aita gogoratzen dut, mutila eskolara zihoalako kexan.
Badirudi bezeroak ez direla askoz hobeak.

source: An old little box. It looks familiar.
target: Kutxa txiki zahar bat. Ezaguna dut.

source: He's harmless, just the tech guy.
He's involved in an event called "The Burning" taking place in The Club.
target: Klubean egingo den "Erreketa" izeneko ekintza batean sartuta dago.

source: I don't know if all these folk are criminals, but they sure like to fight.
target: Ez dakit hauek guztiak gaizkileak ote diren, baina borrokatzea gustuko dute.

source: I guess it's the way to participate in "The Burning" event.
target: Nik uste hau dela "Erreketa" ekintzan parte hartzeko modua.

source:
I know more about Sean's school now.
Tonight's event allows him to select a fighter to become a new disciple.
There are three trials, but basically only the fittest will make the cut.
target:
Sean-en eskolari buruz gehiago dakit orain.
Gaur gaueko ekintzek bere dizipulu berria izango den borrokalaria aukeratzeko parada ematen diote.
Hiru proba daude, baina hobekien prestatutakoek bakarrik gaindituko dituzte.

source: I remember now, I've seen this old box in Sean's fathers school.
target: Orain gogoratzen dut, kutxa hau Sean-en aitaren eskolan ikusi izan dut.

source: I will need a code for this one. For now I have no idea where this leads to.
target: Honetarako kode bat beharko dut. Oraingoz ez dut idearik ere honek nora daraman.

source: I'll need to get there early when it's not too crowded.
target: Goiz joan beharko dut bertara, jende gehiegi egon aurretik.

source: I've found several sentences on the walls of Sean's school. He's brainwashing his disciples with his morbid obsession with strength.
target: Hainbat esaldi ikusi ditut Sean-en eskolako paretetan. Bere dizipuluen burua jaten ari da indarrarekin duen obsesio morboso horrekin.

source: It's difficult to parry the momentum of her kicks, Id better avoid them. I need to watch out for that sweep and Hammer Kick, too.
target: Zaila da bere ostikadak une egokian aldaratzea, ekiditea da hoberena. Bere ekorketa eta Mailu Ostikadarekin ere kontuz ibili behar dut.

source: Nature will eliminate those who do not look out for themselves.
target: Naturak beren burua zaintzen ez dituenak ezabatuko deuseztuko ditu.

source:
Sean has founded his own Kung-Fu school. His disciples use moves I've seen performed by his father back in the day.
They have a real technical background, and can even defend against my fastest strikes.
I need to stay focused.
target:
Sean-ek bere Kung-Fu eskola propioa zabaldu du. Bere dizipuluek erabiltzen dituzten mugimenduak garai batean bere aitak ibiltzen zituenak dira.
Formazio oso teknikoa dute, eta erasorik azkarrenetatik ere babestu daitezke.
Kontzentratuta egon behar dut.

source: Sean, I met him several times when I was a kid. Our fathers knew each others as Kung-fu masters. I can't believe he took part in their deaths.
target: Sean, batzuetan topatu nintzen berekin haurra nintzenean. Gu bion aitek elkar ezagutzen zuten, Kung-Fu irakasle baitziren biak. Ezin dut sientsi beraien heriotzetan parte hartu zuenik.

source: The guy at the entrance told me that I need a special pass if I want to get to Sean.
target: Sarrerako tipoak esan dit sarrera berezi bat behar dudala Sean-engana joateko.

source:
There is a portrait of an elder inside and inscription on the back:

"Be a teacher for a day, be a father for life."
target:
Barruan bere aitaren argazki bat dago eta inskripzio bat du atzeko aldean:

"Izan irakasle egun batez eta izan aita bizi osorako."

source: This USB key should give me access to Jinfeng's personal computer.
target: USB giltza honek Jinfeng-en ordenagailuko sarbidea eman beharko lidake.

source: With this pass I can go directly to "The Burning".

CYCLE
Go on a deep and thoughtful visit through The Cycle, to seek and embrace your own patterns in these works of art.
target:
ZIKLOA
Murgildu zaitez Zikloan egingo duzun bisita sakonean, artelan hauetan zure patroi propioak aurkitu eta onartzeko.

source: Doors to the stairs are locked.

I found this on one of Sean's disciples.
There is a code written on the back of it.
target:
Sean-en dizipulu batek hau zeraman.
Atzeko aldean kode bat du idatzita.

source: I need a key to use this elevator.
target: Giltza bat behar dut igogailu hau erabiltzeko.

source:
I've encountered several disciples from Sean's school here.
They still help each other, surely because Yang asks them to do so.
target:
Sean-en eskolako hainbat dizipulu topatu ditut hemen.
Elkarri laguntzen jarraitzen dute, Yang-ek hala eskatuta ziurrenik.

source:
IDENTITY
Embark on a journey with artists who want to express, explore, and question the concept of identity and what it means to them in today's ever-changing world.
target:
NORTASUNA
Abiatu zaitez bidaian gaur egungo mundu aldakorreko nortasunaren esanahia eta kontzeptua bera adierazi, esploratu eta zalantzan jartzen duten artistekin batera.

source: It opens the doors to the stairs in the atrium.
target: Atarian eskaileretara daraman atea irekitzen du.

source:
Kuroki had a twin.
Must be why she is so obsessed with her own image.
Something terrible seems to have happened to her at some point in her life.
target:
Kuroki-k ahizpa biki bat zuen.
Beharbada horregatik dago bere itxurarekin hain obsesionatuta.
Bere bizitzan zehar zerbait ikaragarria gertatuko zitzaiola dirudi.

source: Kuroki's exhibition is surreal, but this last fight was beyond anything I expected. These people appear to have lost their minds somehow.
target: Kuroki-ren erakusketa surrealista da, baina azken borroka hau espero nuena baino haratago doa. Jende honek burua galdu duela dirudi.

source: Kurokis past is hard to investigate. All I know is that she is Japanese, and rumors tie her to the underworld world.
target: Kuroki-ren iragana ikertzeko zaila da. Dakidan guztia bera Japoniarra dela da, eta txutxumutxuek kaleko krimenarekin lotzen dute.

source: She now runs an art museum. She works there day and night on her most ambitious exhibition to date.
target: Orain arte museo bat zuzentzen du. Orain arteko erakusketarik anbiziotsuenean lanean ari da bertan gau eta egun.

source: Something must have happened to force her into exile here in China.
target: Zerbait gertatuko zen hona Txinara herbesteratu behar izan zenerako.

source:
TWINS
Twins captures the fascinating similarities of identical twins. But just as engaging are the subtle differences between each pair, confirming each twins individuality.
target:
BIKIAK
Bikiak-ek biki berdinen antzekotasun liluragarriak jasotzen ditu. Baina aldi berean zirraragarrik dira bikote bakoitzaren arteko desberdintasunak, biki bakoitzaren indibidualtasuna baieztatus.

source: The place is like a maze, but if I get it right, I just need to get to the top floor to face Kuroki.
target: Lekuak labirintoa dirudi, baina ongi ulertu badut, azken solarira iritsi behar dut Kuroki-ri aurre egiteko.

source:
The strongest opponent I've met so far.
He strikes hard, defends well, and knows how to grapple.
I need to use everything I know if I'm to defeat him.
target:
Inoiz topatu dudan aurkaririk indartsuena.
Gogor kolpatzen du, ongi defendatu eta badaki nola hartu.
Dakidan guztia erabili beharko dut garaitu nahi badut.

source:
There's a lot of security tonight. I guess Sean warned the group of my existence.
Some have blades, I need to be careful.
target:
Segurtasun handia dago gaur gauean. Sean-ek taldeari nire berri emango zion.
Batzuk labanak dituzte, kontuz ibili behar dut.

source: This door has an old lock.
This mask seems to be mocking me.
target: Maskara hau nitaz trufatzen ari dela dirudi.

source: This museum is a brand-new, high-class building, financed privately.
target: Museo hau oso berria da, goi-mailako eraikuntza, finantziazio pribatuarekin egina.

source: Visit the latest exhibition from Kuroki, a vivid and intense voyage throughout the psyche.
target: Bisitatu Kuroki-ren azken erakusketa, psikean zeharreko bidaia bizi eta garbian.

source:
A vow that swears to protect the talismans. It is signed by a group called The Guardians. It looks ancient. My father, Sean's father and Jinfengs names are on it.

The talismans are traps created to corrupt.
The malevolence of their powers are too strong for them to be used.
The Guardians must always serve.
It will train and recruit disciples to pass the burden.
Guarding the talismans will protect the people and the world from corruption.
target:
Talismanak babestuko direla zin egiteko boto batzuk. 'Zaindariak' izeneko talde batek sinatuta dago. Antzinakoa dirudi. Nire aitaren, Sean-en aitaren eta Jinfeng-en izenak bertan daude.

Talismanak galbidera eramateko sortutako tranpak dira.
Beraien botere gaiztoak erabili ahal izateko indartsuegiak dira.
Zaindariek beti zerbitzatu behar dute.
Dizipuluak errekrutatu eta entrenatuko dira karga hori pasatzeko.
Talismanak gordetzeak jendea eta mundua zorigaitzetik salbatuko du.

source:
Alongside my father, Jinfeng was highly renowned and respected among the citys Kung-Fu masters.
She was always the first to defend the underprivileged and helpless, and always held a strong sense of justice.
I don't know why she turned against them, but she will pay for that.
target:
Nire aitarekin batera, Jinfeng hiriko Kung-Fu maisuen artean oso ezaguna eta errespetatua zen.
Beti zen behartsu eta babesgabeen alde egiten zuen lehenengo, eta beti izan zuen justizia zentzu handia.
Ez dakit zergatik egin duen beraien kontra, baina garesti ordainduko du.

source:
Analysts, managers, developers; all sorts of people work here at The Corporation.
They all have one thing in common They are too well-trained to be simple office workers.
target:
Analistak, kudeatzaileak, garatzaileak; mota guztietako jendeak egiten du lan Korporazioan.
Gauza bat dute komunean: entrenatuegiak daude bulegoko langile arruntak izateko.

source:
Charity Art Auction
Kuroki's Museum is heavily funded by Jinfeng.
This is a flyer promoting the collaboration between the two entities, and the auction they held to raise money for the grand opening.
target:
Arte enkante benefikoa
Kuroki-ren Museoak Jinfeng-en diru asko jasotzen du.
Bi entitateen arteko elkarlana goraipatzen duen paper bat da hau, eta lekuaren irekierarako dirua lortzeko egin zuren enkante handia aipatzen da.

source:
I found another one of these old boxes in Jinfeng's safe.
The box is empty.
target:
Mota honetako beste kutxa zahar bat aurkitu dut Jinfeng-en kutxa gotorrean.
Kutxa hutsik dago.

source: I need a keycard to use this elevator.
target: Txartel bat behar dut igogailu hau erabili ahal izateko.

source:
Instead of having to go on the top of the building, I need to go deeper underground to find Jinfeng.
I sense a strong calling coming from the depths of this place.
target:
Eraikinaren goienera igo beharrean, lurpera joan behar dut Jinfeng aurkitzeko.
Leku honen sakonenetik dei indartsu bat nabari dut.

source: Jinfeng has her office on the top floor of the building.
target: Jinfeng-ek bere bulegoa eraikin honen goieneko solairuan du.

source: Jinfeng's personal computer. I need the password to unlock it.
target: Jinfeng-en ordenagailu pertsonala. Desblokeatzeko pasahitza behar dut.

source:
Now she has become the head of a vast and extremely powerful corporation.
She's still helping those in need, albeit with greater means, but her sudden increase in wealth is very suspicious.
target:
Orain izugarri handi eta boteretsua den korporazio bateko burua da.
Oraindik behar dutenei laguntzen die, baliabide gehiagorekin, baina bere bapateko aberastasuna susmagarria da.

source:
She is one of Jinfeng's trusted lieutenants.
She lectured me about The Guardians, the group my father, Jinfeng, and the other masters belonged to back in the day.
Why did my father never tell me about this group?
target:
Jinfeng-en ordezkari fidelenetako bat da.
Zaindariei buruz irakatsi zidan, garai batean nire aita, Jinfeng eta beste maisu batzuk kide izan ziren taldea.
Zergatik ez zidan aitak talde hau inoiz aipatu?

source:
Silent, cold blooded fanatics.
They ambushed me in the depths of The Tower.
target:
Ixilak, odol hotzeko fanatikoak.
Dorrearen sakonean segada ipini zidaten.

source:
The Dawn Group

The symbol and name of the secret order founded to wipe out the Guardians.
target:
Egunsentia Taldea

Zaindariak desegiteko sortutako ordena honen irudi eta izena.

source:
The Sanctuary Opening
Yang's Sanctuary. Looks like it was financed by Jinfeng's company.
There's a list of traditional Chinese healing methods used at the place.

"The Corporation is proud to continue their partnership with The Sanctuary, a place dedicated to traditional healing of the worlds most severe illnesses. The Sanctuary has aided the medical community in treating several untreatable conditions with astonishing results."
target:
Santutegiaren irekiera
Yang-en Santutegia. Jinfeng-ek enpresak finantzatu zuela dirudi.
Hemen erabiltzen diren Txinako sendatze metodo tradizionalen zerrenda bat dago.

"Korporazioa harro dago Santutegiarekin duen elkarlanarekin jarraitzeaz, munduko gaixotasunik larrienak sendatzeko modu tradizionalei eskeinitako lekua. Santutegiak medikuntza komunitateari lagundu dio tratatu ezin ziren gaixotasunak tratatu eta emaitza harrigarriak lortuz."

source:
The five kung-fu schools destroyed eight years ago, and the four masters killed.
They were called The Guardians.

Jinfeng betrayed them, she planned it all right here with Yang and the others.
target:
Orain dela zortzi urte deuseztatu ziren bost kung-fu eskolak, eta bertan lau maisuak hil zituzten.
Zaindariak deitzen zieten.

Jinfeng-ek traizionatu zituen, hemen planeatu zuen dena Yang eta besteekin.

source: The highest building in the city, located in a recently constructed district.
target: Hiriko eraikinik altuena, berriki eraikitako barruti batean.

source: "He who has Kung-Fu and Wude, makes the other know he can break him. And the other doesnt want to fight anymore. This is Wude."
target: "Kung-Fu eta Wude-a duenak, bestari xeheatu dezakeela jakinarazten dio. Eta besteak ez du borrokan jarraitu nahi. Hori da Wude-a."

source:
1. REN  - HUMANITY
2. LI  - DEFERENCE
3. ZHI  - WISDOM
4. YI  - JUSTICE
5. XIN  - SINCERITY
target:
1. REN  - GIZATASUNA
2. LI  - ADEITASUNA
3. ZHI  - JAKITURIA
4. YI  - JUSTIZIA
5. XIN  - ZINTZOTASUNA

source: A refuge for the terminally ill. It grants them access to a range of traditional healing methods to try and alleviate their pain.
target: Gaixotasun terminalak dituztenentzako babesgunea. Beraien minak arintzen laguntzeko sendatze metodo tradizionalak eskura jartzen dizkien leku bat.

source: An article about Yang and The Sanctuary.
target: Yang eta Santutegiari buruzko artikulu bat.

source: An old key adorned with the symbol of a flower.
target: Lore baten ikurra duen giltza zahar bat.

source: He disappeared with his wife and daughter when I was still a child. He came back years later and murdered my father in cold blood.
target: Bere emazte eta alabarekin desagertu zen ni oraindik haurra nintzela. Urte batzuk beranduago itzuli eta nire aita odol hotzean hil zuen.

source: He now lives above the city and runs a traditional healing center, but he doesn't appear to be in touch with the world.
target: Orain hirian bizi da eta medikuntza tradizional zentro bat zuzentzen du, baina ez dirudi kanpoko munduarekin inongo erlaziorik duenik.

source: I need a keycard to get through this door.
target: Ate hau zeharkatzeko txartel bat behar dut.

source: I sense a deep sadness here. I wonder what it means to Yang?
target: Hemen tristura handia nabari dut. Zer esan nahi ote du Yang-entzat?

source: It has gained a strange reputation over the years thanks to its so-called medical miracles.
target: Urteetan zehar ospe arraro samar bat irabazi du, mediku-mirari deitutakoei esker.

source: The key of the aromatic garden.

The talismans are gifts created to serve.
The greatness of their powers is too strong to be left unused.
The group must never become extinct.
It will strike again and retrieve the gifts.
Studying and using the talismans will benefit all people.
target:
Talismanak zerbitzatzeko sortutako opariak dira.
Beraien boterearen handitasuna indartsuegia da erabili gabe uzteko.
Taldea ezin da inoiz desagertu.
Berriz eraso egin eta opariak berreskuratuko ditu.
Talismanak eralibi eta ikertzeak jende guztiari onura ekarriko dio.

source:
This is a symbol I saw in Yangs office.
It represents the five moral values.
target:
Hau da Yang-en bulegoan ikusi nuen ikurra.
Bost balio moralak irudikatzen ditu.

source:
This is an ancient scroll signed by The Alchemists.
A new symbol has been recently added (The Dawn).
target:
Alkimistek sinatutako antzinako pergaminoak.
Ikur berri bat gehitu diote berriki (Egunsentia).

source: This is where everything ended, once and for all. Everything.
target: Hemen bukatu zen dena, behin betiko. Den-dena.

source:
This was on Yangs tree, above two tombs. Two lost souls.
This was the beginning of the end for him.
target:
Hau Yang-en zuhaitzean zegoen, bi hilobiren gainean. Galdutako bi arima.
Hau izan zen bere amaieraren hasiera.

source: Today marks the eighth anniversary of the Sanctuary that sits high above the city. Founded by a former martial artist, it has welcomed many patients over the years, providing a full range of traditional healing techniques.
target: Gaur da hiriaren gainean dagoen Santutegiaren zortzigarren urtemuga. Arte martzialetako maisu izandako batek sortua, paziente askori eman die ongi etorria urteetan zehar, sendatze teknika tradizionalen aukera zabala eskeiniz.

source: Trained and raised by my father and Sifu. We were close, he taught me a lot over the years.
target: Nire aita eta Sifurekin entrenatu eta hazitakoa. Hurkoak ginen, asko irakatsi zidan urteetan zehar.

source: With this keycard I can go directly to Yang's office.
target: Txartel honekin Yang-en bulegora zuzenean joan nahiteke.

source: Yang has been keeping a very close eye on Fajar's mental and physical health over the years.
target: Yang-ek Fajar-en osasun mental eta fisikoa oso hurbiletik jarraitu du urte hauetan zehar.

source:
Yang suffered a great loss, a loss that made him bitter and blinded him.
Could things have been different?
target: Yang-ek galera handia sufritu zuen, zakarrago bihurtu eta itsutu zuen galera.

source:
We welcome the lost, the despairing, and the broken spirits." says the founder of The Sanctuary.
"Such a place should have existed long before I founded it."
target: Galdutako, etsitako eta puskatutako espirutei ongi etorria ematen diegu. dio Santutegiaren sortzaileak.

key: Nik sortu baino askoz ere lehenagotik existitu behar zuen leku bat."

source: After a Game Over or Give Up you can choose the level you want to start from among the ones you have unlocked.
target: Joko Amaiera edo Amore Ematearen ondoren desblokeatu dituzun mailetatik zeinetan hasi nahi duzun aukeratu dezakezu.

source: After each death the pendant increases its Death Counter.
target: Heriotza bakoitzaren ondoren, zintzilikarioak Heriotz Kontagailuan gehituko du.

source: As the years increase, the pendant gradually loses its power and the coins eventually break.
target: Urteak pasa ahala zintzilikarioak bere boterea galtzen du eta azkenean txanponak puskatu egingo dira.

source: Avoid: time slows down for the duration of the attack. Any hit on an enemy during this window will stun them.
target: Ekidin: erasoak iraun bitartean denbora moteldu egiten da. Tarte honetan etsai bati emandako edozein kolpek nahasita utziko du.

source: Avoiding attacks regenerates a small amount of structure.
target: Erasoak ekiditeak oreka apur bat berreskuratzen laguntzen du.

source: Deflect: the attack will be parried, leaving an opponent open to a counter-attack or throw.
target: Baztertu: erasoa aldaratu egingo da, erasotzailea kontraeraso edo jaurtitze baterako arriskuan utziz.

source: Deflecting / Parrying attacks prevents you from having your structure broken.
target: Erasoak baztertu/aldaratzeak zure oreka galtzea ekidingo du.

source: Guardbreak attacks deal a massive amount of structure damage. You should always try to avoid them.
target: Eraso batzuk ezin dira blokeatu eta desoreka handia sortzen dute. Horiek ekiditen saiatu beharko zenuke beti.

source: If you take too many hits structure will eventually break, leaving you open to attacks for a short time.
target: Kolpe gehiegi hartzen badituzu, azkenean oreka galduko duzu eta edozein eraso hartzeko arriskuan egongo zara.

source: Once a skill has been bought, you can consolidate it to be unlocked across all your runs.
target: Abilezia bat behin erosita, partida guztietan eskuragarri egoteko finkatu ahal izango duzu.

source: Once their structure is broken, take them down.
target: Oreka galduarazten diezunean, bota itzazu lurrera.

source: Once there are no more coins remaining, you cannot rise again, and your next death leads to a Game Over.

source: Several stuns in a row can lead to a dazed state where opponents cannot defend themselves for several seconds.
target: Aurkari bati behin baino gehiagotan nahasmendua eragiteak zorabiatzea eragin dezake, hainbat segundoz etsaia ezin defendatzea eraginez.

target: Aurreko partidetan desblokeatutako abilezia eta hobekuntzak galdu egingo dira. Baina itemak edo Detektibe Arbeleko informazioa, baita betirako desblokeatutako abileziak ere, mantendu egingo dira.

source: Some attacks can be punished by performing the right defense: deflect or avoid.
target: Eraso batzuk zigortu egin daitezke defentsa ona egiten bada: baztertu edo ekidin.

source: Structure is impacted each time you're hit.
target: Jotzen zaituzten aldi bakoitzean orekan nabarituko da.

source: Structure represents your ability to defend yourself and fight.
target: Orekak zure babesteko eta borrokatzeko gaitasuna irudikatzen du.

source: Stunned opponents cannot defend themselves, leaving them open to attacks or throws.
target: Zorabiatutako etsaiak ezin dira defendatu, erasotzeko edo jaurtitzeko arriskuan geldituz.

source: Then, when rising, you age the same number of years.
target: Gero, berpizten zarenean, zure adina zenbaki horren berdina izango da.

source: They are indicated by an enemy's glowing limbs.
target: Etsaien gorputz-adar disdiratsuen bidez adieraziko dira.

source: They are indicated by glowing limbs and a red circle.
target: Etsaien gorputz-adar disdiratsuen eta zirkulu gorri baten bidez adieraziko dira.

source: Throws cannot be blocked or deflected. You can only avoid them.
target: Jaurtiketak ezin dira blokeatu edo baztertu.

source: XP allows you to buy skills for your current run.
target: unekoak uneko partidarako abileziak erosteko balio du.

source: You can break an enemy's structure by attacking or deflecting/parrying their attacks.
target: Etsai baten oreka puska dezakezu, eraso eginez edo bere erasoak baztertuz/aldaratuz.

source: You gain XP by defeating enemies.
You'll start the level at the youngest age you were when you reached it.
target: Mailara ailegatu zinen adin txikienarekin hasiko duzu maila.

target: Ezarri zure zailtasuna eta hasi zure mendekua hasieratik.

Arenas only. Reduce the intensity of light sources to prevent in game sharp light transitions.

source: A combo leading to a series of lightning fast attacks.
target: Eraso azkarren segida batera daraman konboa.

source: A powerful blow in the solar plexus that stuns the enemy for a long time.
target: Plexu solarrean emandako kolpe boteretsu bat, etsaia denbora luzez zorabiatuko duena.

source: A powerful blow to break your opponents weapon (doesn't work for blades).
target: Zure aurkariaren arma puskatzeko gai den kolpe indartsua (xafladunekin ez du funtzionatzen).

source: After a successful parry, knock your enemy down with a quick throw.
target: Aldaratze arrakastatsu baten ondoren, eraitsi etsaia jaurtiketa azkar batekin.

source: Attack on a pushed enemy to follow them up and deliver a powerful series of strikes.
target: Egin eraso bultzatutako etsai bati kolpe indartsu segida batekin jotzen jarraitzeko.

source: Attack on a pushed enemy to follow up and knock them down.
target: Egin eraso bultzatutako etsai bati jarraitu eta lurrera botatzeko.

source: Attack with a short range that can avoid high attacks.
target: Eraso altuak ekidin ditzaken irismen motzeko erasoa.

source: Combo leading to a powerful high kick capable of knocking down multiple enemies.
target: Zenbait etsai lurrera bota ditzakeen ostikada altu indartsu batean bukatuko den konboa.

source: Continue to use a weapon until it breaks completely.
target: Jarraitu arma bat erabiltzen erabat puskatu arte.

source: Disarm an opponent with a one-handed weapon.
target: Esku bakarreko arma duen etsaia armagabetu.

source: Dodge towards your target just after a hit to grab them and invert your positions.
target: Kolpe baten ondoren, saihestu kolpatu nahi zaituenaren aldera eta aldatu zuen posizioak.

source: Engage attack with important forward movement.
target: Aurreranzko mugimendu handi bat egiten duen erasoa.

source: Fast and evasive strike that leaves your back facing the enemy.
target: Eraso azkar eta iheskorra, etsaiari bizkarra emanez utziko zaituena.

source: Fast strikes to daze and incapacitate your enemy for a few seconds.
target: Eraso azkarrak nahasmendua eragin eta etsaia segundo batzuz ezgaitzeko.

source: For bat weapons. A direct attack to daze your enemy.
target: Bate gisako armentzat. Nahasmendua eragiteko eraso zuzena.

source: For bladed weapons. A damaging slash attack.
For staff weapons. A wide attack capable of knocking down multiple enemies.
target: Makilentzat. Hainbat etsai lurrera botatzeko gai den eraso zabala.

source: Grab a stunned enemy to throw them in the direction you want.
target: Hartu zorabiatutako etsai bat nahi duzun norabidean jaurtitzeko.

source: Hook that can withstand attacks during its buildup.
target: Kargatzen den bitartean erasoak jasan ditzakeen kakoa.

source: Learn skills through Death or Shrines.
target: Ikasi abileziak Heriotz edo Erlikien bidez.

source: Parry at the right moment to catch an item thrown at you.
target: Aldaratu une egokiak bota dizuten objektua hartzeko.

source: Perform a slide kick while running that knocks down enemies.
target: Ostiko irristari bat egin korrikan zoazen bitartean etsaiak lurrera botatzeko.

source: Powerful strike to the enemy's knee, knocking them down for a while.
target: Etsaiaren belaunera eraso boteretsua, denbora batez lurrera botako duena.

source: Quick, ducking punch that avoids high strikes.
target: Makurtuta zaudela, eraso altuak ekiditeko ukabilkada azkarra.

source: Straight strike that applies a destructive push to your enemy.
target: Etsaiari bultzada hauskor bat ematen dion kolpe zuzena.

source: Threaten an enemy with your weapon.
Throw an item, weapon, or object directly from the ground.
target: Jaurti item, arma edo objektu bat lurretik zuzenan.

source: Unleash a powerful punch that stuns any enemy.
target: Eman etsaia zorabiatuko duen ukabilkada boteretsu bat.

source: Unlock stats boosts by finding Shrines.
While on the ground, parry to counter your enemy's attack.
target: Lurrean zauden bitartean, aldaratu erasoa kontraerasoa egiteko.

source: You've reached the limit of your pendant power, your next death will be your last.
target: Zure zintzilikarioaren boterearen mugara iritsi zara, zure hurrengo heriotza azkena izango da.

source:
To our players: 
We are an independent games studio based in France. Our team has created Sifu with love and respect for Chinese Kung Fu culture, and we sincerely hope that you will like it. We will listen to your feedback attentively and try out best to improve the game accordingly. Have a great time!
target:
Gure jokalariei:
Frantzian finkatuta dagoen joko independenteen estudio bat gara. Gure taldeak Txinako Kung Fu kulturari dion maitasun eta errespetutik sortu du Sifu, eta benetan espero dugu zuek gustuko izatea. Zuen ekarpenak arretaz entzungo ditugu eta modu berean hobetzen saiatuko gara. Ongi pasa ezazue!

source: Alternate your options and use your whole moveset to maximize your score gain.
target: Txandakatu aukerak eta erabili zure mugimendu arsenal guztia ahalik eta puntu gehien lortzeko.

source: Be aggressive, favor efficiency and early kills over style or safety.
target: Izan oldarkorra eta lehenetsi eraginkortasuna eta heriotz goiztiarrak estilo edo segurtasunaren gainetik.

source: Chain various actions without inactivity or getting hit to increase the multiplier.
target: Lotu hainbat ekintza gelditu gabe edo inork zu jo gabe biderkatzailea handitzeko.

source: Choose wisely which target to prioritize to gain time.
target: Aukeratu zein jomuga lehenetsi denbora irabazteko.

source: Clear the {0} {1} as fast as possible
Climb walls, jump gaps and vault to reduce your travel time.
target: Eskalatu paretak, gainditu zuloak eta egin jauzi zure bidaia denbora murrizteko.

source: Having no enemies in the zone greatly boosts your capture rate.
target: Eremuan etsairik ez izateak zure konkista erritmoa izugarri handitzen du.

source: If available, keep your Focus to maximize your damage on targets.
target: Eskuragarri badago, mantendu Fokatzea jomugetan mina maximizatzeko.

source: If available, keep your Focus to quickly deal with strong enemies.
target: Eskuragarri badago, mantendu Fokatzea etsai indartsuekin azkar bukatzeko.

source: If available, use your Focus moves to increase your capture rate.
target: Eskuragarri badago, erabili Fokatze mugimenduak zure konkista erritmoa handitzeko.

source: If available, use your Focus moves to increase your multiplier.
target: Eskuragarri badago, erabili Fokatze mugimenduak zure biderkatzailea handitzeko.

source: Isolate dangerous enemies to avoid fighting them in groups.
target: Isolatu etsai arriskutsuak beraien aurka taldean borroka egitea ekiditeko.

source: Stay active and quickly kill enemies without getting hit to increase your capture rate.
target: Mantendu aktibo eta hil etsaiak azkar ukitua izan gabe zure konkista erritmoa handitzeko.

source: Stay as young as you can for {0} {1}
Stay calm, dont get yourself overwhelmed or surrounded by enemies
target: Mantendu lasai, ez zaitzala egoerak gainditu edo etsaiek inguratu

source: Use Focus attacks (if available), pushes and knockdowns to keep enemies under control.
target: Erabili Fokatze erasoak (eskuragarri badaude), bultzadak eta eraisteak etsaiak kontrolpean edukitzeko.

source: Use the environment to eliminate targets quickly.

target: Erabili armak eta ingurunea mina maximizatzeko.

source: A STUNNED or PARRIED enemy can be thrown in any direction.
target: ZORABIATUTAKO edo ALDARATUTAKO etsai bat edozein norabidetan jaurti daiteke.

target: Apuntatu jaurti nahi duzun norabidea Ezker Palanakarekin.

target: Oztopo baxuak jauzi eginez gainditu eta pareta batzuk eskalatu daitezke.
